WEBVTT

00:08.551 --> 00:11.051
<i>My name is Melinda Gordon.</i>

00:12.680 --> 00:15.473
I just got married,
just moved to a small town,

00:15.474 --> 00:17.517
<i>just opened up an antique shop.</i>

00:17.518 --> 00:20.018
I might be just like you.

00:20.396 --> 00:22.397
Except from the time
that I was a little girl,

00:22.398 --> 00:25.400
I knew that I could talk to the dead.

00:25.401 --> 00:26.859
It's all right, honey.

00:26.860 --> 00:29.362
Earthbound spirits,
my grandmother called them,

00:29.363 --> 00:30.863
<i>the ones who have not crossed over</i>

00:30.864 --> 00:32.949
<i>because they have
unfinished business with the living.</i>

00:32.950 --> 00:35.670
<i>And they come to me for help.</i>

00:35.869 --> 00:40.389
To tell you my story,
I have to tell you theirs.

